---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-charcoal to-gray-900">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-accent-yellow">Meet Your Meme God Mentor</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <img src="/memegod.jpg" alt="Meme Tutor" class="rounded-full w-64 h-64 mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-accent-green">
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center md:text-left">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-accent-orange">Professor Memestopher</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">With over 9000 viral memes under his belt, Professor MemeGod has been making the internet laugh since the days of Ming Mega. His mission? To train the next generation of meme lords and spread joy across the digital realm!</p>
        <ul class="text-lg space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
            <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-green mr-2" />
            <span>Certified Dank Meme Creator</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
            <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-green mr-2" />
            <span>PhD in Memology from Meme University</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
            <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-green mr-2" />
            <span>Featured in "Know Your Meme" Hall of Fame</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
            <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-green mr-2" />
            <span>Proudly Elsiesian</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
            <Icon name="mdi:check-circle" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-green mr-2" />
            <span>Proudly Lavis Hater</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>